  "type": "mcq",
  "stem": "<p>A hemisphere is half of a sphere. If a hemisphere has a radius of <math alttext=\"27\"><mn>27</mn>\n</math> inches, which of the following is closest to the volume, in cubic inches, of this hemisphere?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
